section.basequipment-not
  .wrapper
    h2.basequipment__title Не входят в базовую комплектацию:
    .basequipment__categories-roster.basequipment__categories-roster--single
      .basequipment__category.basequipment__category--not
        ul.basequipment__category-list
          each item in equipmentNotData
            li(class= item.content ? "basequipment__item" : "basequipment__item basequipment__item--empty")
              button.button.accordion-button.basequipment__item-name(type="button")= item.name
              .basequipment__item-content.accordion-content
                if item.content
                  p= item.content
